379
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,791
♪ LIVE IT UP EVERY DAY ♪

380
00:22:13,875 --> 00:22:16,625
- ♪ ALL MY LIFE HERE ON THE
GROUND ABOUT TO RUN AND NOW ♪

381
00:22:16,708 --> 00:22:19,333
♪ I FIND I MUST
ASK MYSELF WHY ♪

382
00:22:19,416 --> 00:22:21,958
♪ 'CAUSE SOMETHING IS STIRRING ♪

383
00:22:22,041 --> 00:22:25,000
♪ I FEEL IT WHISPERING IN ME ♪

384
00:22:26,416 --> 00:22:27,541
♪ SOME DAYS I WAKE UP ♪

385
00:22:27,625 --> 00:22:29,250
♪ BUT MY HEART'S
STILL SLEEPING ♪

386
00:22:31,875 --> 00:22:34,500
♪ AND I KNOW IT'S TIME
