387
00:22:34,583 --> 00:22:39,500
♪ AND I KNOW IT'S TIME TO FLY ♪

388
00:22:39,583 --> 00:22:42,500
♪ AND LIKE THE WIND
WE WILL RUN ♪

389
00:22:42,583 --> 00:22:44,333
♪ THROUGH THESE SKIES ON HIGH ♪

390
00:22:44,416 --> 00:22:47,458
♪ WITH OUR GOAL IN SIGHT ♪

391
00:22:47,541 --> 00:22:50,083
♪ WE WILL RUN
WITH ALL OUR MIGHT ♪

392
00:22:50,166 --> 00:22:55,250
♪ TOMORROW AND TODAY
WILL NEVER EVER PASS US BY ♪

393
00:22:55,333 --> 00:22:58,416
♪ WE WILL NOT STOP NOW ♪

394
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:01,166
♪ KEEP YOUR HEART ALIVE
AND KEEP SURVIVING ♪

395
00:23:01,250 --> 00:23:04,791
♪ AND CROSS
THE FINISH LINE ♪

396
00:23:04,875 --> 00:23:06,500
♪ LET IT GO ♪

397
00:23:06,583 --> 00:23:08,250
- ♪ YOU CAN RUN, YOU CAN STOP
YOU CAN JUMP, YOU CAN CRAWL ♪

398
00:23:08,333 --> 00:23:10,750
♪ YOU CAN LOSE, YOU CAN WIN ♪

399
00:23:10,833 --> 00:23:13,750
♪ YOU CAN SING, YOU CAN SHOUT
TAKE A BREATH, LET IT OUT ♪

400
00:23:13,833 --> 00:23:16,791
♪ LIVE IT UP EVERY DAY ♪

401
00:23:17,958 --> 00:23:19,666
- Yamato: THE CICADAS
ARE OUT EARLY.

402
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:22,000
THEY'RE CHIRPING,
AND IT'S ONLY JUNE.

403
00:23:22,083 --> 00:23:24,083
I'M SUCH AN IDIOT, AREN'T I?

404
00:23:24,166 --> 00:23:26,125
ALWAYS RUNNING MY BIG MOUTH.

405
00:23:26,208 --> 00:23:28,291
- Suzuka: IT'S BEEN MUCH HOTTER
THAN USUAL THIS YEAR.

406
00:23:28,375 --> 00:23:30,500
MAYBE THEY CAME OUT EARLY
THINKING IT WAS SUMMER ALREADY.

407
00:23:30,583 --> 00:23:32,000
- HUH?
- JUST A THOUGHT.

